WEBVTT

00:02:58.474 --> 00:03:00.607
And "A colder melon skin."

00:03:01.503 --> 00:03:02.657
Period.

00:03:02.681 --> 00:03:03.795
(Laughter)

00:03:03.819 --> 00:03:06.231
Far better use of those
kellianderson.com letters,

00:03:06.255 --> 00:03:07.878
I'm sure you'll agree.

00:03:09.545 --> 00:03:13.650
This is a dumb game,
but it underscores a belief I have,

00:03:13.674 --> 00:03:15.361
that the world is full of order

00:03:15.385 --> 00:03:18.180
that doesn't necessarily
deserve our respect.

00:03:18.204 --> 00:03:22.557
Sometimes, there's meaning, justice
and logic present in the way things are.

00:03:23.163 --> 00:03:24.905
But sometimes there just isn't.

00:03:25.579 --> 00:03:29.775
I think that the moment we realize this
is the moment we become creative people,

00:03:29.799 --> 00:03:32.563
because it prompts us to mess things up